    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and is mated to a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical longevity has been prioritized: the VANOS system has been fully serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with steel plates to ensure chassis rigidity. The drivetrain is rounded out by a functional M-Variable Differential Lock, providing excellent lateral traction. The suspension features upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and oil pressure\u2014remain within factory specifications. This is a robust, mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
