      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-cared-for daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a brilliant depth and shine, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The premium leather upholstery shows gentle softening and light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, but remains free of rips or stains. All interior electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it features a comprehensive service log with recent oil and filter changes, a firm brake pedal feel, and a smooth-shifting transmission. The engine pulls cleanly throughout the rev range with no unusual noises or vibrations. With four matching tires showing deep tread and a chassis that feels tight and responsive, this car is ready for its next chapter without the need for immediate investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
