      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape! It runs beautifully and has been well-loved over the years. If you're looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready for many more miles, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions or come by to take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
