      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, delivering an authentic analog performance experience. The chassis remains rigid with recent subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry is dialed for precision cornering. While the car shows honest wear commensurate with its age, the powertrain is robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sorted specimen ready for the B-roads.",
